name: Honeysuckle
content: Honeysuckle high in the tree
忍冬在高高的枝头绽放
You let the world live under you
世界尽在你的脚下
Like you're some good royalty
气质高雅犹如皇室贵族
当你在盛夏怒放的时候
That heat you let him wonder
势头正劲 无人敢接近
But you never let him sink in his teeth
你令人引发遐想 却从不叫人沉迷
No one can touch you when you move
你摇曳身姿的时候 无人敢接近
